content:
The accounts payable balance as at 30 September 2022 mainly entailed consulting fees to 企業管理諮詢公司 (Management Consulting Company) of CNY2.3M and professional fees to 信用中和會計師事務所(特殊普通合夥) (ShineWing Certified Public Accountants) of CNY14.0K.

SUMMARY: Used entities '企業管理諮詢公司' (CNY2.3M) and '信用中和會計師事務所(特殊普通合夥)' (CNY14.0K) which constitute major portions of the total accounts payable of CNY11.8M.
